item.title: CVE-2023-1864|2023-06-07T20:43:17.256Z -- fanuc -- roboguide-handlingpro
item.description: FANUC ROBOGUIDE-HandlingPRO Versions 9 Rev.ZD and prior is vulnerable to a path traversal, which could allow an attacker to remotely read files on the system running the affected software.
